  "instructions": [
    "Heat the earthenware bowl over medium heat on the stovetop.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the gochugaru and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the cod fish pieces and cook until they are opaque.",
    "Add the dum, coconut milk, fish stock, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes or until the stew has thickened.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired."
